snippet.title: Crown Wars | Forge your weapons
snippet.description:
In the midst of the war of crowns, every battle is decided by steel and fire. Fearless knights wield legendary weapons. Choose your allies wisely.

Fight Darkness with Sword and Wit!

Crown Wars will be released on March 2024 on Xbox Series X|S,Playstation 5 and PC.

Wishlist now: https://nacon.me/CWSteam
Get it for Xbox:  https://nacon.me/3TjgjtP
